================================================================================
Components intentionally NOT included in this repository
================================================================================

For licensing, privacy, and size reasons the following are excluded from this
public repository and must be supplied or regenerated by the operator:

  - Model weights (LLM GGUF, STT/TTS/embedding ONNX) — obtain from upstream
    under their own licenses; placed under ai_models/ at runtime.
  - Custom synthesized TTS voices — not redistributed.
  - Fine-tuning / RAG training corpora derived from external LLM outputs or
    from academic-only datasets (e.g. AI-Hub) — excluded; such data carries
    redistribution restrictions and is not published here.
  - Child conversation/audio data — never committed; stored only on-device.
  - Runtime secrets (parent-portal PIN, device env) — never committed.

================================================================================
Korean-history grounding content (assets/history/)
================================================================================

The Korean-history grounding corpus under assets/history/ is used at runtime
for factual grounding. Operators redistributing this project should verify the
provenance and licensing of this content for their use case.

